{"tid":251644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打女朋友口講好愛你","createTime":"2017-05-21T06:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T10:30:04.000Z","uid":71208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f8270b6596fda6c112f3d62b6744ebe4d17273","tid":251644,"uid":71208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"我女朋友以前成日會主動講好掛住我 好愛我 會每日問我做過咩黎 好關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (未一齊既時候)<br />\n<br />\n但一齊左之後 就愈黎愈小呢D 我問佢係咪變左 佢又話唔係 每次都要我主動講掛住佢 佢先會講 (利申 以前唔係咁)<br />\n<br />\n依家我對佢就愈黎愈好 相反佢對我就唔會好似之前咁 咁主動 有好多野應承之後 都無做過 <br />\n<br />\n佢係咪已經唔愛我了？"},{"pid":"95fddd7f71b7d5d0e0b3043cab5820b2b9d9a160","tid":251644,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\nEx 日日都會講話愛我一千十萬分<br />\n最後都發現我比人帽左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c671124b07dabd74bea567a87827f2a1bf3e30","tid":251644,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"愛唔係講出來，係做出來"},{"pid":"bd3e1678e0303124a7adbf15cc76497de0efefb4","tid":251644,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛唔係講出來，係做出來</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"fda51de72dd35eba03daf5f301766346687db902","tid":251644,"uid":118065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"男人老狗care 埋呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e323ddd5950855b54cbe3e0e456171aab8a1e643","tid":251644,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"俾人帽左啦"},{"pid":"41153ee342eddb6d0c396cdc510dfc219c7ae67a","tid":251644,"uid":71208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗care 埋呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁應該係care d咩？"},{